-education outside the classroom (including field studies) in initial
-teacher training provision. We consulted TDA as part of our
-preparations for the
-project.</p><br><notus-date day="7" month="6" year="2006" textMonth="Jun"></notus-date><b>7 Jun 2006 : Column 619W</b><br><h3 align="center" style="text-transform:uppercase"><a name="06060874000003">Transport</h3><h3 align="center"><a name="06060874000023">Civil
