-system for motoring 
-<br><notus-date day="7" month="6" year="2006" textMonth="Jun"></notus-date><b>7 Jun 2006 : Column 620W</b><br>offences. The proposals are contained in the Road Safety Bill, currently
-before
-Parliament.</p><p><a name="06060874000238">The
